                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body" align="center">
                     <p>PBC Sunbeam School believes that a child is a gift from God created from His image and endowed with unique talents and abilities which must be nurtured in accordance with the highest standards of excellence and in conformance with God’s plans.</p><br><p>
“Train up a child the way he should go. When he grows up, he will not depart from it.”
